org.divxdede.text.formatter

Interface PatternFormatter.IndexableArgumentNameSpace

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PatternFormatter.ArgumentNameSpace
    Enclosing class:
    PatternFormatter

    public static interface PatternFormatter.IndexableArgumentNameSpace
extends PatternFormatter.ArgumentNameSpace
    IndexableArgumentNameSpace is a namespace that can define which argument must be used for formatting a specified conversion's identifier. This kind of namespace handle argument's choice and the pattern can't try to specify any index informations.
